1. *Spustite* se sa brda (Descend from the hill).
2. Njegovi su roditelji ga *spustili* u grad (His parents sent him to the city).
3. Oni su *spustili* letjelicu na zemlju (They landed the aircraft on the ground).
4. Ona je *spustila* loptu sa krova (She dropped the ball from the roof).
5. *Spustite* se na razinu mora (Descend to the level of the sea).
6. Oni su *spustili* njegovu ocjenu (They lowered his grade).